.6","text":"Yet have I set my king upon my holy hill of Zion.","year":-1042},{"id":"recc58Ewax0Jj5bpM","ref":"Ps.2.7","text":"I will declare the decree: the LORD hath said unto me, Thou art my Son; this day have I begotten thee.","year":-1042},{"id":"recBrJsBfsmMAqqwM","ref":"Ps.2.8","text":"Ask of me, and I shall give thee the heathen for thine inheritance, and the uttermost parts of the earth for thy possession.","year":-1042}]}
